{
  "stem": "71.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were supposed to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We registered to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there was a camp in Italy that-- from Italy, you know, they had [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But this-- thsi transport was stopped, so they could not accommodate us, and they send us to Germany to Landsberg am Lech.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's where I met Ben.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He came when we came, an American.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Yeah, before we came to Landsberg, we stopped in Munich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we all got out from the-- from the train and danced the Hora.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the depot, which was our greatest satisfaction, we-- we all sang [INAUDIBLE], and we danced the Hora.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then they took us on trucks and brought us to Landsberg am Lech.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that's where we lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then I met Ben, and he left later the camp and-- because we looked for my brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We met some people that were with my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And this was the only brother that we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And one said to me-- one man said to me, if anybody from this camp is alive, it would be Joseph.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because he kept us alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "When we were laying in despair on the-- on the bunk beds, he would sing for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He had a beautiful voice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they even told me the songs that he was singing for them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So 100%, he's alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started looking in all the hospitals in all the camps, and we couldn't find him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then one day, somebody came and told us that they found a grave in Feldafing, which was near Munich, a camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went there, and I have a picture of that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We put later-- later we put a [NON-ENGLISH] for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
